= SPH Summary

::[font-size:85%;]

* Set initial conditions \(v_i\)

::[height:0.5em;]::

* Compute values
** - Density: \(\displaystyle \rho_i = \sum_{j=0}^{N-1} m_j \, W_h^{poly6}(\|p_i-p_j\|)\)
** - Pressure: \(\mathrm{p}_i = s\,(\rho_i-\rho_0)\)

::[height:1em;]::

* Compute forces
** - \(F_{weight}=m_i\;g\)
** - \(\displaystyle F_{pressure}=-\frac{m_i}{\rho_i} \, \sum_{\substack{j=0 \\ j\neq i}}^{N-1} m_j \, \frac{\mathrm{p_r}_j+\mathrm{p_r}_i}{2\,\rho_j} \; \nabla  W_h^{spiky}(\|p_i-p_j\|)\)
** - \(\displaystyle F_{viscosity}=m_i\,\nu \, \sum_{\substack{j=0 \\ j\neq i}}^{N} m_j \frac{(\mathrm{v}_j-\mathrm{v}_i)}{\rho_j}\;\triangle W_h^{spiky}(\|p_i-p_j\|)\)

::[height:1.5em;]::

* Time integration: \(v_i^{k+1}=v_i^k + \Delta t\;\left(F_{weight}+F_{pressure}+F_{viscosity}\right)/m_i\)


